As I’m understanding your question, no.
Masterful Replication turns all of your artifacts into the same artifact.

There’s no window, even between turns, for you to gain the benefit of turning all of your artifacts into Timesifter.

No one gets priority before the Upkeep phase begins. And all “until end of turn” effects clear during the Cleanup step.
This is the general case. You can add other cards that *might* help, like Brudiclad. But even the most Jank-enabler of all time, Sundial of the Infinite, doesn’t help.
